fulltitle: Jim Hall and Bob Brookmeyer - I Should Care (1987)
title: Jim Hall and Bob Brookmeyer - I Should Care (1987)
description: Jim Hall and Bob Brookmeyer playing 'I Should Care' in the Guildhall, Bath, UK, during the 1987 Bath Festival.
